      • updateStockRecipeMode

        public void updateStockRecipeMode()
        Sets updatedStock to a copy of the current stock. Set's all quantities to 9999 temporarily.

      • initializeRemainingIngredients

        public void initializeRemainingIngredients()
        Takes the Stock and adds each ingredient that doesn't exist in the table view into it. Furthermore adds ingredients with 0 units left, but prevents the user from adding it to the MenuItem.
